\ls36\ilvl0
\f0\b0\fs28 \cf2 \cb4 \kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 \outl0\strokewidth0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
\outl0\strokewidth0 \strokec2 A\'a0
\f3\fs25\fsmilli12600 \cb14 DriftReport
\f0\fs28 \cb4 \'a0with: features analyzed, how many drifted, severity distribution, top 10 drifted features\cb1 \
